By Brokencool

There are a lot of great cover songs on YouTube; there are also a lot of terrible ones. We have pulled together the worst of the worst for these 15 Covers of Rap Songs That Will Make You Cringe. Whether it be an acoustic Macklemore cover by two European kids or a grandfather covering Chief Keef, this list is proof positive that not everyone should own a webcam or cell phone.
